Description: Functions to download, clean, and analyze daily and monthly
    climatological data from Mexico's National Weather Service (SMN), including
    robust retrieval, parsing, and aggregation utilities. The package provides
    reproducible pipelines for station metadata, daily time series, and monthly
    summaries with completeness checks.
